<!-- STORY PAGE -->
<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-bg-text">{{ page.title }}</div>
  <div class="page-eyebrow">ACHE — The Foundation</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">
    <em>Why we exist.</em>
    {{ page.title }}
  </h1>
</div>

<!-- Intro Split -->
<div class="story-intro reveal">
  <div class="story-intro-img">
    <span class="story-intro-img-text">ACHE</span>
  </div>
  <div class="story-intro-content">
    <div class="story-intro-eyebrow">The Beginning</div>
    <h2 class="story-intro-title">
      <em>It started with</em>
      Two Words.
    </h2>
    <div class="story-intro-body">
      {{ page.content }}
    </div>
    <a href="{{ routes.collections_url }}" class="btn btn-black" style="margin-top:1.5rem">Shop the Collections →</a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- The Verse -->
<div class="story-verse-block reveal">
  <div class="story-verse-ref">John 11:35 — The Founding Verse</div>
  <div class="story-verse-text">"Jesus wept."</div>
  <div class="story-verse-cite">The shortest verse. The deepest theology.</div>
</div>

<!-- The Pillars -->
<div class="story-pillars reveal">
  <div class="story-pillar">
    <div class="story-pillar-num">01</div>
    <div class="story-pillar-title">The Ache is Sacred</div>
    <div class="story-pillar-body">We refuse to skip the grief. Every collection leans into a real human experience — burden, lament, covenant. These are not abstract concepts. They are Monday morning. They are 3am.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="story-pillar">
    <div class="story-pillar-num">02</div>
    <div class="story-pillar-title">Scripture on the Skin</div>
    <div class="story-pillar-body">Every garment carries the Word — not as decoration but as declaration. The verse on your chest. The promise on your cuff. The hidden tag at your neck that only you know is there.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="story-pillar">
    <div class="story-pillar-num">03</div>
    <div class="story-pillar-title">Quality as Theology</div>
    <div class="story-pillar-body">400gsm heavyweight fleece — heavy enough to feel like an embrace. Every detail is intentional. Nothing cheap. Because the Word deserves to be carried in something that lasts.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="story-pillar">
    <div class="story-pillar-num">04</div>
    <div class="story-pillar-title">Community — The Carry</div>
    <div class="story-pillar-body">ACHE is not a brand you follow. It's a community you join. People who know what it means to carry something heavy — and to find each other in the weight.</div>
  </div>
</div>

